# Keep host build artifacts out of the Docker build context so `COPY backend/ .`
# / `COPY frontend/ .` never overwrite the image's freshly-installed, platform-
# correct dependencies (host is glibc; images are musl/alpine). Also avoids
# shipping a stale incremental TS cache that makes tsc emit an empty dist/.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.angular
.git
**/.env
**/.env.*
